<section class="features-section">
  <h2>Application Features</h2>
  
  <p>This web application is designed to provide full CRUD functionality (Create, Read, Update, Delete) in a user-friendly and secure environment. Below are the key features included in this project:</p>

  <ul class="features-list">
    <li><strong>Create Items:</strong> Easily add new entries using a clean and simple form. All required fields are validated.</li>
    <li><strong>Read/View Items:</strong> Display a complete list of stored items in a responsive table format. Includes pagination and search (optional).</li>
    <li><strong>Update Items:</strong> Edit existing items directly from the list page using pre-filled forms for efficiency.</li>
    <li><strong>Delete Items:</strong> Remove individual items securely with confirmation prompts to prevent accidental deletions.</li>
    <li><strong>User Authentication:</strong> Supports Local and GitHub login using Passport.js to ensure secure access to app features.</li>
    <li><strong>Protected Routes:</strong> Only authenticated users can create, edit, or delete items.</li>
    <li><strong>Search Functionality:</strong> Easily filter items in real-time (if implemented).</li>
    <li><strong>Responsive Layout:</strong> Fully mobile-friendly UI with clean design powered by custom CSS.</li>
    <li><strong>Error Handling:</strong> Friendly messages for validation, 404 errors, and server issues.</li>
    <li><strong>Deployed Online:</strong> Hosted using Render or another cloud platform for easy access and sharing.</li>
    <li><strong>Reusable Layout:</strong> Uses Handlebars layout (`main.hbs`) for consistent header, navigation, and footer across all pages.</li>
  </ul>
</section>
